## Purpose:
Define all canonical folder paths used across the Soulfra codebase. Allows consistent references regardless of script or daemon execution context.

---

## Example:
```json
{
  "agents": "./agents/",
  "loops": "./loop/",
  "logs": "./logs/",
  "config": "./config/",
  "memory": "./memory/",
  "mirror_shell": "./mirror-shell/",
  "queue": "./agents/suggestions/"
}
```

## Use In:
- `unified-soulfra-server.js`
- All daemons
- Frontend loaders (for dynamic routing)
